# Project Structure Guide

## Main Directories
- **Source code**: [src](mdc:src) - All application source code
- **App routes**: [src/app](mdc:src/app) - Next.js App Router pages and layouts
- **Components**: [src/components](mdc:src/components) - Reusable UI components
- **Collections**: [src/collections](mdc:src/collections) - Payload CMS collections
- **API layer**: [src/server](mdc:src/server) - tRPC routers and server logic
- **Public assets**: [public](mdc:public) - Static files and images

## Key Configuration Files
- **Next.js**: [next.config.js](mdc:next.config.js) - Next.js configuration
- **Package management**: [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Dependencies and scripts
- **TypeScript**: [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- **Styling**: [tailwind.config.mjs](mdc:tailwind.config.mjs), [postcss.config.js](mdc:postcss.config.js)
- **UI components**: [components.json](mdc:components.json) - Shadcn/UI configuration
- **Payload CMS**: [src/payload.config.ts](mdc:src/payload.config.ts) - CMS configuration

## Specialized Directories
- **Access control**: [src/access](mdc:src/access) - Permission functions
- **Migrations**: [src/migrations](mdc:src/migrations) - Database schema changes
- **Global configs**: [src/globalConfigs](mdc:src/globalConfigs) - Payload global configurations
- **Providers**: [src/providers](mdc:src/providers) - React context providers
- **Utilities**: [src/utilities](mdc:src/utilities) - Helper functions and utilities
